## Quick start

```bash
python -m venv venv && source venv/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"
cp env.example .env
uvicorn asgi:application --reload --port 8001 --lifespan on
```

Server: http://localhost:8001
MCP endpoint: http://localhost:8001/mcp
OAuth discovery: http://localhost:8001/.well-known/oauth-authorization-server

## Layout

```
src/
├── server.py              # FastMCP instance + tool mounts
├── app.py                 # Starlette factory
├── config/settings.py     # Pydantic settings (env-driven)
├── core/                  # auth, errors, http_client, telemetry, handlers
├── middleware/            # auth + telemetry middleware
├── views/                 # health, oauth discovery, landing
└── tools/                 # your tools live here
```

## Adding a tool

```bash
remote-mcp add tool my_tool
```

Then mount in `src/server.py`:

```python
from src.tools.my_tool import my_tool_router
mcp.mount(my_tool_router)
```

